 WHAT is the most important thing to consider when choosing a bra: colour, length, fabric or size? The answer is no. Those features are important, but the most important things to consider when picking a bra are the bust size and band. For so many women, a bra is a fashion item because of the Iift and roundness it gives to the breast. But a bra is more than a fashion item. It is also an item of comfort. So, how can you know the right bra to wear? Check out the following steps.